Create a variable `width` with the const keyword and give it a value of 10.
Create a variable `height` with the const keyword and give it a value of 20.
Create a variable `area` with the const keyword and give it the value of the product of the variables `width` and `height`.

A similar example:
```javascript
const a = 10;
const b = 20;
const c = a * b;
```
